Treatment:.

in antioxidants.
Benefits:
• Enhance immunity, promote self-healing ability
• Promote Blood Circulation and lymphatic drainage
• Improving energy levels by balancing Yin-Yang (Positive and negative energy)
• Cleanses the body and promotes acid-base balance
• Mental and Physical Relaxation
• Relieves Water Retention
• Scalp Detox
• Stress Relief
• Pain relief

These are steps they will take in Day 1, 3, and 5:
Steps 1 – Pressure points using basalt stones – 15 minutes
Step 2 – MLD with Vaccum probe- 15 minutes

and leave for 15 min
Step 4 – EMS 24 program no- 6(Detox program) – 45 minutes
Step 5 – Liver Compression technique – 20 minutes
Step 6 - Herb infused Steam inhalation - 10 minutes
